=head1 DESCRIPTION

The video features set for the meeting. Applies to all attendees.

If you specify C<MeetingFeatures:Video:MaxResolution:None> when you
create a meeting, all API requests that include C<SendReceive>,
C<Send>, or C<Receive> for C<AttendeeCapabilities:Video> will be
rejected with C<ValidationError 400>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 MaxResolution => Str

The maximum video resolution for the meeting. Applies to all attendees.

Defaults to C<HD>. To use C<FHD>, you must also provide a
C<MeetingFeatures:Attendee:MaxCount> value and override the default
size limit of 250 attendees.



